    "Smaller" : {

    },
    "Software like After Effects, DaVinci Resolve, and Premiere Pro renders Hebrew left-to-right, flipping the character order. Pre-reversing the text compensates — when the app lays it out LTR, it looks correct." : {
      "comment" : "Reversal explanation"
    },
